:

1. *Malu* je nosio u školu. (He carried the small one to school.)
2. *Malu* štenad je najbrže rastuća stvar. (The small puppy is the fastest growing thing.)
3. *Malu* kuću je napravio za sebe. (He built a small house for himself.)
4. Ona je dala *malu* pomoć. (She gave a little help.)
5. *Malu* bebu je nosila u kolicima. (She carried the little baby in a stroller.)